<div class="mt-4 px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-6xl px-6 py-6 sm:py-8 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="mx-auto py-6 sm:py-8 text-pretty text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight text-gray-950 sm:text-6xl">Stay up to date</h1>
    <h2 class="mx-auto py-6 sm:py-8 max-w-3xl text-2xl font-medium text-gray-500">The best way to find out more about WS10 is on this website or by signing up to our email newsletter.</h2>
    <div class="mx-auto py-6 sm:py-8 max-w-3xl">
      <script async data-uid="16ceeabcab" src="https://ws10.kit.com/16ceeabcab/index.js"></script>
    </div>
    <h2 class="mx-auto py-6 sm:py-8 max-w-3xl text-2xl font-medium text-gray-500">You can also <a href="https://strava.com/clubs/ws10" class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey">join the ws10 club on Strava</a>, or <a href="https://facebook.com/ws10.run" class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey">follow the ws10.run Facebook Page</a> to find out about future events (if their algorithms decide to show it to you).</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-6xl px-6 py-6 sm:py-8 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl lg:max-w-4xl text-xl/7 text-gray-600">Here's a bunch of questions I've been asked a few times in one way or another. Got a different question? <a href="mailto:matt@ws10.run" class="font-medium text-brand-brown hover:text-brand-grey underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline">Send me an email</a> and Iâ€™ll get back to you as soon as I can.</p>
    <div class="mt-20">
      <dl class="space-y-16 sm:grid sm:grid-cols-2 sm:space-y-0 sm:gap-x-6 sm:gap-y-16 lg:gap-x-10" data-controller="faq">
        <div>
          <dt class="text-xl/7 font-medium text-gray-900" id="how-fast">How fast do I need to be?</dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-xl/7 text-gray-600">The timing will stop at 1 hour 20 minutes. If you can finish a parkrun in less than 35 minutes, without almost dying, you can probably complete a WS10 in the available time.</dd>
        </div>

        <div>
          <dt class="text-xl/7 font-medium text-gray-900" id="slower-than-that">What if I'm slower than that?</dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-xl/7 text-gray-600">If you can't finish in 1 hour 20 minutes but you're still keen to participate, let me know. I'm open to having an earlier start time for slower runners.</dd>
        </div>

        <div>
          <dt class="text-xl/7 font-medium text-gray-900" id="how-to-register">How do I register?</dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-xl/7 text-gray-600">You only need to register on the site once, and then you can show up to any event. To register go to <%= link_to "the sign up page", sign_up_path, class: "font-medium text-brand-brown hover:text-brand-grey underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline" %> and fill in your details. Don't forget to click on the confirmation link in your email afterwards!</dd>
        </div>

        <div>
          <dt class="text-xl/7 font-medium text-gray-900" id="no-confirmation-email">I tried to register, why didn't I get a confirmation email?</dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-xl/7 text-gray-600">The most likely reason is that it went to spam, check your spam for an email from <span class="font-medium">matt@ws10.run</span>. Mark it as not spam (and then try again if the confirmation link has expired). The next most likely reason is a typo in your email address (don't worry, it can happen to anyone). Register again and make sure you're typing it correctly.</dd>
        </div>

        <div>
          <dt class="text-xl/7 font-medium text-gray-900" id="donate">Are you on Strava / Facebook / X (Twitter) / Instagram / Snapchat / LinkedIn / Tumblr / WhatsApp / TikTok / YouTube / Reddit / WeChat / Weibo / Kakaotalk?</dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-xl/7 text-gray-600">Yes. Yes. No. No. No. No. No. No. No. No. No. No. No. No.</dd>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-xl/7 text-gray-600">The home for WS10 is here, on the WS10 website and in the WS10 email list. That's the best way to find out what's going on. I cross post to the <a href="https://www.strava.com/clubs/ws10.run" class="font-medium text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey">ws10.run Club on Strava</a> and the <a href="https://facebook.com/ws10.run" class="font-medium text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey">ws10.run Page on Facebook</a> but I can't guarantee what the algorithm will show you so your best bet is to sign up to the WS10 email list at the top of this page.</dd>
        </div>

        <div>
          <dt class="text-xl/7 font-medium text-gray-900" id="how-can-i-help">How can I contribute to WS10?</dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-xl/7 text-gray-600">There are several ways you can contribute:
            <ol class="list-decimal list-inside">
              <li>Come along and participate! Having a friendly group of people makes it worth organising.</li>
              <li>Invite others! Bring along some friendly, enthusiastic people to run with us.</li>
              <li>Volunteer occasionally! Perhaps you can do the timing one month? Or bring an esky and some water bottles? Let me know if you're keen to help and we can figure something out!</li>
              <% if repeat_runner? %>
                <li><%= link_to "Support financially!", support_path, class: "font-medium text-brand-brown hover:text-brand-grey underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline" %> Your contribution helps improve the event for everyone.</li>
              <% end %>
            </ol>
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div>
          <dt class="text-xl/7 font-medium text-gray-900" id="why-free">How much does it cost to participate?</dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-xl/7 text-gray-600">The event is completely free! Contributions from regular attendees are gratefully received, get in touch if you'd like to know more.</dd>
        </div>

        <div>
          <dt class="text-xl/7 font-medium text-gray-900" id="other-question">I have a different question, how can I get in touch?</dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-xl/7 text-gray-600">The best way is to <a href="mailto:matt@ws10.run" class="font-medium text-brand-brown hover:text-brand-grey underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline">send me an email</a>. I can also be contacted on Strava or you can message the <a href="https://facebook.com/ws10.run" class="font-medium text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey">ws10.run page</a> on Facebook Messenger.</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
